code: export default function SortSchedule(dateList){dateList.sort(function(a,b){var year1=a.slice(0,4);var year2=b.slice(0,4);if(year1!==year2){if(year1>year2)return 1;else return-1;}else{var month1=a.slice(5,7);var month2=b.slice(5,7);if(month1!==month2){if(month1>month2)return 1;else return-1;}else{var date1=a.slice(8,10);var date2=b.slice(8,10);if(date1!==date2){if(date1>date2)return 1;else return-1;}else{return 0;}}}});return dateList;}
